{
  "title": "Working with Media",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Working with Media</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\"> How to play linear video in your projects, and how to integrate Unreal's rendered frames into virtual production and broadcast scenarios. </p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Working with Media\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/197a67bb-0c57-42dc-b521-d7373f14274c?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/197a67bb-0c57-42dc-b521-d7373f14274c?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/197a67bb-0c57-42dc-b521-d7373f14274c?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"10\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"9\"><!----><block-markdown ngh=\"2\"><div class=\"block-markdown\"><p>With Unreal Engine, you can integrate your pre-recorded media into your project seamlessly and share your rendered frames live or recorded. Use Unreal Engine's real-time rendering for shooting real-time visual effects, broadcasting on air or to tape, and rendering on complex arrangements of physical displays for live performances. With end-to-end color management and the ability to synchronize multiple media sources, Unreal can fit into the technical pipeline for any virtual production or live event.</p>\n\n<p>The following sections contain information on the tools and workflows to make the most of media and rendered frames for your projects and audience.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"integratingmedia\">Integrating Media</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A short overview of using Bink Video to show movies.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:bink-video-for-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Bink Video for Unreal Engine\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/cb5eed4a-53e1-4775-a7be-27d1909e195a/00-topic-bink.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Working with Media Playback functionality in Unreal Engine.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:media-framework-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Media Framework\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/215f5f75-1287-4053-b627-1c3b1ae76415/topicimage_mediaframework.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Contains information about getting professional quality video into and out of the Unreal Engine.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:professional-video-io-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Professional Video I/O\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/179f366b-2194-43c0-83b5-6788abcc8d17/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"The Camera Calibration plugin provides users with simplified tools and workflows to calibrate a camera and lens in the editor.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:camera-lens-calibration-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Camera Lens Calibration\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/e2e7209f-ed00-4833-a12c-55f66c39fbc8/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"With in-camera VFX you can shoot real-time visual effects during a live action film shoot with an immersive LED volume.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:in-camera-vfx-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"In-Camera VFX\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/bc181056-670a-4bc3-8f3c-3b4680b8085d/topicimage_incameravfx.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"nDisplay renders your Unreal Engine scene on multiple synchronized display devices.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:rendering-to-multiple-displays-with-ndisplay-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Rendering to Multiple Displays with nDisplay\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/5a4d508e-5596-4444-bbd9-9fd5c9c44c21/ndisplay_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Share GPU data and bypass the CPU across Unreal Engine instances, nDisplay devices, and other graphics applications.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:texture-share-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Texture Share\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/5cd2d910-f2d4-49b1-b086-f490b1d86816/texture_share_topic_image.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Composite footage of users into a virtual space with Mixed Reality Capture\" href=\"#unreal-doc:mixed-reality-capture-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Mixed Reality Capture\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/13d761ec-b4e2-477d-ad66-032f1878abe7/mrdevelopment_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n\n<h2 id=\"communicatingwithmediacomponents\">Communicating with Media Components</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"The DMX Plugin enables Unreal Engine use for live events and permanent digital installations.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:dmx-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"DMX\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/524a8111-d99c-4161-9b48-5226220c884c/dmx-topicimg.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Control multiple remote machines from one application with Switchboard.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:switchboard-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Switchboard\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/3a270949-14b3-4bcf-9fde-bf88d085d296/topic-image-switchboard.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Stage Monitor reports events from multiple instances of Unreal Engine\" href=\"#unreal-doc:stage-monitor-with-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Stage Monitor\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/6c17407d-7c7d-42e4-aa77-6a7e7f846eb4/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Monitor, calibrate, and view incoming timed data from multiple sources through Live Link or SDI.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:timed-data-monitor-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Timed Data Monitor\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/8375efd0-98f3-42f3-9c6d-153a87cdfe14/image_0.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n\n<h2 id=\"managingcolor\">Managing Color</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An overview of Working Colour Space in Unreal Engine\" href=\"#unreal-doc:working-color-space-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Working Color Space\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/9ebe0e82-c2be-47b6-b6b1-3a9ae9ea3e61/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Ensure color consistency across projects with OpenColorIO.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:color-management-with-opencolorio-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Color Management with OpenColorIO\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ef0bc18a-5379-466c-8aa0-9e01a779e43d/ocio_heroimage.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Details on applying color grading using volumes on your level's environment with Color Correct Regions.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:color-correct-regions-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Color Correct Regions\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/141281dc-3cce-4ddd-ac18-a22ca54332e8/topicimage_ccr.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n\n<h2 id=\"capturingmedia\">Capturing Media</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Guide to taking in-game screenshots of environments and gameplay.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:taking-screenshots-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Taking Screenshots\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ec33036f-0c08-4848-99d3-b696b2f5d5e1/00-topic-image-taking.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A look at how to use the Stereo Panoramic plugin to capture VR images.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:panoramic-capture-tool-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Panoramic Capture Tool\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/fbe3b2c3-31e3-4280-bb91-40a00324e507/spe_topic_image_00.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n</div></block-markdown><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></blocks-renderer></div><!----></div></article><!----><div class=\"col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block d-print-none\"><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----></main>",
